---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="Privacy Policy for Balance Performance Physiotherapy."
>
	<PageHero
		title="Policy"
		highlight="Privacy"
		breadcrumb="Privacy Policy"
	/>
	<section class="rich-content">
		<div class="container">
			<p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>
			<p>Balance Performance Physiotherapy (&ldquo;we&rdquo;, &ldquo;us&rdquo;, &ldquo;our&rdquo;) is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use and safeguard your personal data.</p>

			<h2>Who we are</h2>
			<p>Balance Performance Physiotherapy, 113 Gauden Rd, London SW4 6LE. We are registered with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) and act as the data controller for any personal information you provide to us.</p>

			<h2>Information we collect</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Contact details (name, email, phone, postal address)</li>
				<li>Clinical and medical information provided during assessment and treatment</li>
				<li>Insurance and payment details where relevant</li>
				<li>Website usage data (cookies, analytics)</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>How we use your information</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>To provide you with clinical treatment and aftercare</li>
				<li>To process bookings, cancellations and payments</li>
				<li>To communicate with you about your care</li>
				<li>To comply with legal and regulatory obligations</li>
				<li>To improve our services</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Sharing your information</h2>
			<p>We share personal data only where necessary — for example with your GP or consultant (with your consent), your insurer, or approved technology providers who support the running of our clinic. We never sell your data to third parties.</p>

			<h2>Your rights</h2>
			<p>You have the right to access, correct or request deletion of the personal data we hold about you. You also have the right to object to or restrict processing, and to lodge a complaint with the ICO.</p>

			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>For any privacy-related questions please email <a href="mailto:enquiries@balancephysio.com">enquiries@balancephysio.com</a> or call 020 7627 2308.</p>

			<p><em>This placeholder content should be replaced with a policy reviewed by your legal advisor before launch.</em></p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
